quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  70,19,"Diggah seehadayti baakerliiy, qaraarakolih (qambaxxaglih) anuk ginniime"
  70,20,usuk umaane kaa xagte tet tekkek qaraarako li kinni (qaxbaxxaagite)
  70,21,Kaadu maqaané kaa xagteeh gaddalitek kaxxa gabâ gibda li kinni
  70,22,Salat abá koh raqtuh immay
  70,23,Woh umman sinni salaatih baguk kate waa mara kinni
  70,24,Kaadu usun yimixxige cakki (maglab kinnuk) maalut kak yan mara kinni
  70,25,Kallaca tu malii kee kallace waa tu malih
  70,26,Kaadu usun cisab kee galtoh ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) nummaysa mara
  70,27,Kaadu usun sinni Rabbih digaalák meesita mara
  70,28,"Tama meesih kah meesitaanam, diggaluk ken Rabbih digaalá yaamineenim mali (baggibda mali)"
  70,29,Kaadu usun sinni sammooma (sambooba) dalwak dacrisa mara
  70,30,"Sinni gennaaqoh agabuu kee sinni say naqoosay ken gabá timlike akke waytek, toysa diggah usun qeemu maloonuuy, yassacakken mara hinnon"
  70,31,"Tokkel tamahak kalihim faxeeh, gurrise mari, woo mari usun caddok taturleela kinni"
  70,32,Kaadu usun sinni amaanootaa kee sinni xagna dacrisa mara kinni
  70,33,"Kaadu usun sinni sumaaqittel soolaah, wohul diggi iyya mara kinni"
  70,34,Kaadu usun sinni salat le waktil dacrisa mara kinni
  70,35,"Woo mari jannootah addal massakaxxa leeh, ruffu iyya"
  70,36,Nabiyow koroosite mari fillitte kadeedisak koo fanah edde yardem maca lee
  70,37,Kok migdaa kee gura le kabul horta hortah gaca mara akkuk
  70,38,"Kulli seehadayti keenik, Yalli waara niqmat le jannat ise culsaamah sangeelaa"
  70,39,"Aleey caagid usun elle yakkalen inna hinna, diggah nanu usun yaaxigeenimik ken ginne. (woh daacoyta kinnuk)"
  70,40,Ayrô mawqooqii kee ayrô kormaami Rabbil (Yalli isi nafsi edde faxak) xiibita diggah nanu dudda linoomul
  70,41,"Keenik yayse mara ciggiilisnaamal, kaadu hebeltô seehadayti keenik nek mayassaqqa, ken bayisnam fannek abe nee kaltam matan"
  70,42,"Toysa usun Sinni baatilit giirisoonay ken ixxic, kaadu sinni addunyal digritoonay ken ixxic ken ayróy (woh Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) kah xagnisimeenit ongoorowwu iyyaanam fanah"
  70,43,"Magooqak sissikuk yawqen ayró, addunyal sinni yallittey xeet kee cooxuk tanî fanah tet yaqbudoonuh asassakuk kah gexak sugen innah"
  70,44,"Intiita keenik meesih rammitak buraa kee qunxaané ken buulta, woh addunyal kah xagnisimak sugen ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) kinni"
  71,1,"Diggah, nanu Nabii Nuuc kay marâ fanah kaa rubneh, qansarissa digaalá keenih tamaatek naharal, ku mara meesis iyyaanamal"
  71,2,"Nabii Nuuc iyyeh: yi maraw! Diggah anu siinih meesisso kak baxxaqqa le farmoyta kinniyo"
  71,3,"Yalla uqbudaay qibaada kaah caglisa, kaadu kaak meesitaay, yamri oggola"
  71,4,"Tohul sin dambitte siinih cabeleeh, qumri siinih wadirroyse le yimixxige waktî fanah, Diggah Yalli mekle wakti (Raba kinnuk) yamaate waqdi, mawadirroysima, isin woh yaaxige mará akkinnitoonuy iimaanâ fanah asissikuk tenen"
  71,5,"Nabii Nuuc iyyeh:yi Rabbow diggah, anu inni mara kol yaamanoonuh baraay laqó ken seeceh"
  71,6,Tokkel Yi seeco tu keenih mossinna kudimik sá
  71,7,"Kaadu diggah, anu keenih seecinnaanih waqdi dambi keenih cabtuh sinni feeraari sinni aytiitat heeniih (axcem yaabbeenimik) sinni sarat yumbududeeniih, (yoo yableenimik) koroosannul yeedeeniih, kaxxa mariinoh kaxxa mariiniten iimaan oggolaanamak"
  71,8,"Tohih lakal diggah, anu xongolo fayya haak keenih seece"
  71,9,"Tohih lakal diggah, anu xongolo fayya keenih heeh, tutuccah tutuccu keenit exce"
  71,10,"Tokkel sinni Rabbil dambi cabti essirita keenik exce, diggah usuk maggom dambi cabti li kinnik"
  71,11,"Yallal tuduureeniih, dambi cabti kaal esseritteenik, sittallakleh rob siinih ruube le"
  71,12,"Kaadu maaluvy xalay farakka siinih heele, kaadu wahoobah yan basaatin siinih heele, kaadu weeqaytitte siinih heele"
  71,13,Maca liton Yallih nabnak kah meesite waytaanam
  71,14,Nummah Yalli ranko rankoh sin ginek
  71,15,Yalli malcina qaran sittak amol massoowak elle gine inna matablaanaa
  71,16,"Kaadu alsá ken (Qaranwa kinnuk) addal diifu abeeh, ayró ifa faanus abe"
  71,17,Kaadu Yalli baaxok sin gineeh aysubukiyyah sin yuysubuke
  71,18,"Tohuk lakal teetit sin gacsaah, Qhiyaamah ayro teetik sin yayyaaqe ayyaaqiyyah"
  71,19,Kaadu Yalli baaxó fidó siinih abe
  71,20,Farakka le gitittel tet bagul gexxoonuh
  71,21,"Nabii Nuuc: yi Rabbow diggah usun (boola le mara kinnuk) yamri cineeniih, le maaluu kee le xalay finqak sa tu kah osse wayta abbottii kee gaddaloola katyen iyye"
  71,22,Kaadu usun kaxxa uma maláh malsen
  71,23,"Kaadu sinni yallitteh qibaadá macabina sittak iyyen, kaadu Waddiiy, Suwaaqaay, Yaqhusuvy, Yaquuqh kee Nasri deqsitta numtinwellitteh qibaadá macabina sittak iyyen"
  71,24,Kaadu nummah maggo mara finqiseenihik ta daalimiinih finqak sah tu mossin iyye Nabii Nuuc isi Rabbik
  71,25,"Usun aben dambitteh sabbatah leet yunxuqsumeeniih, girá culsumen, tokkel usun Yallak kalah cateynit magennon"
  71,26,"Kaadu Nabii Nuuc: yi Rabbow baaxô bagul koroosite marak inkittuy mutuccu iyya macabin iyye"
  71,27,"Diggah atu ken cabtek ku naqoosa makkoyse loonuuh, maxalan umeynay kaxxa koroosannu le akke waytek"
  71,28,"Nabii Nuuc: yi Rabbow yoo kee yi xaleynaay, yi buxá moominiinih anuk cule maraa kee, lab moominiin kee say moominiinih inkih dambi cabaay, daalimiinih baatik sa tu mossin iyye"